Class PropertyStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.core.commands.common.EventManager
      • org.eclipse.jface.preference.PreferenceStore

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.jface.preference.IPersistentPreferenceStore, org.eclipse.jface.preference.IPreferenceStore
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public class PropertyStore
extends org.eclipse.jface.preference.PreferenceStore
    This class implements a store for project and plug-in properties. The idea is to provide project-specific settings that default to plug-in wide settings. It is based on the class described in the article Mutatis mutandis - Using Preference Pages as Property Pages by Berthold Daum.
    Author:
    Ernesto Posse
